{"ts": "2026-06-09T17:16:53.291314+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "I've read the README and examined the project structure. Here's the important thing to know: **this project does not have a Flutter web target.** The web component (`web/`) is a separate **AngularDart** progressive web app, not a Flutter Web app. The Flutter project (`mobile/`) targets Android and iOS only.\n\nThere is no `flutter build web` pathway in this repository, and the AngularDart web build does not produce output under `build/web/` (that's a Flutter Web convention).\n\n---\n\nHere are the actual instructions from the README for each target:\n\n### AngularDart Web Target (the actual web app)\n\n```bash\n# 1. Install Dart SDK for web (Flutter's bundled Dart is NOT suitable)\n#    → See https://webdev.dartlang.org/tools/sdk#install\n\n# 2. Install webdev tooling\npub global activate webdev\n\n# 3. Rename the TMDB config (required before any build)\ncd core/lib/src && mv tmdb_config.dart.sample tmdb_config.dart && cd ../../..\n\n# 4. Fetch dependencies for the web project\ncd web && pub get\n\n# 5. Serve for development\nwebdev serve\n\n# 6. Produce a release build (outputs to web/build/, NOT build/web/)\nwebdev build --release\n```\n\n### Flutter Mobile Target (Android / iOS)\n\n```bash\n# 1. Install Flutter\n#    → See https://flutter.io/docs/get-started/install\n\n# 2. Rename the TMDB config\ncd core/lib/src && mv tmdb_config.dart.sample tmdb_config.dart && cd ../../..\n\n# 3. Fetch dependencies\ncd mobile && flutter pub get\n\n# 4. Run\nflutter run\n```\n\n---\n\n### Why there's no `build/web/` output\n\nThe `build/web/` directory is what `flutter build web` produces. This repo predates Flutter Web support (it was built with **Flutter 1.0**) and intentionally keeps web as a separate AngularDart project for 40% code-sharing via the `core` package. If you specifically want a Flutter Web build, you'd need to add web support to the `mobile/` Flutter project yourself — the repository doesn't provide that out of the box.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 1438, "prompt_tokens": 16676, "total_tokens": 18114, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 964, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 13888}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "mimo-v2.5-pro", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "a75c1d9f52aa47c9a92c5f497526ea62", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ead62-6b1e-73e2-ac1f-34b12ae8d20a-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 16676, "output_tokens": 1438, "total_tokens": 18114, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 13888}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 964}}}}]}}}
